name: 6 Tribal Shields - Taliba Tribe
description:
Taliba ~ (Tribe of Knowledge)

Extreme gnosis inhabits the Spirit of the Ancestors and current generations of this Tribe.

They have finely honed the Art of Knowing and this is utilized in their every waking and slumbered moment.
The seers See and communicate the Truth of Love, Time and Space.
They are not often wrong but frequently misunderstood. This they know too.

Warriors of World's here and those gone by.
